'''弗瑞德里克·麥可·林恩'''（{{lang-en|Fredric Michael Lynn}}，{{bd|1952年|2月3日|}}），為美國職棒大聯盟的中外野手。生涯曾效力過紅襪、天使、金鶯、老虎與教士等隊。他在1975年同時拿下聯盟新人王和聯盟MVP，成為大聯盟史上第一位同年獲得這兩個獎項的球員。

2002年，林恩入選紅襪隊名人堂。2007年，他入選大學棒球名人堂。<ref>[http://www.cstv.com/sports/m-basebl/stories/070507aab.html Fred Lynn Officially Inducted into College Baseball HOF] {{Wayback|url=http://www.cstv.com/sports/m-basebl/stories/070507aab.html |date=20171201081953 }} CSTV.com, July 5, 2007</ref>
==職業生涯==
===波士頓紅襪===
1974年9月5日，林恩登上大聯盟。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.retrosheet.org/boxesetc/1974/B09050BOS1974.htm |title=Milwaukee Brewers 4, Boston Red Sox 3 |website=[[Retrosheet|Retrosheet]] |date=September 5, 1974 |access-date=2020-09-29 |archive-date=2021-03-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210308130328/https://www.retrosheet.org/boxesetc/1974/B09050BOS1974.htm }}</ref>該年他出賽15場比賽，合計43個打數敲出18支安打。

1975年，還只是大聯盟菜鳥的林恩便迎來了生涯大爆發。該年他的打擊率高達3成31，並敲出21轟與105分打點。這年他不僅在打擊王排名第二，還同時拿下金手套獎、美聯新人王漢美聯年度MVP大獎。他也成為第一位同年拿下新人王和年度MVP的球員。其中6月18日他更是敲出3支全壘打與10分打點。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.retrosheet.org/boxesetc/1975/B06180DET1975.htm |title=Boston Red Sox 15, Detroit Tigers 1 |website=[[Retrosheet|Retrosheet]] |date=June 18, 1975 |access-date=2020-09-29 |archive-date=2022-03-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220326232901/https://www.retrosheet.org/boxesetc/1975/B06180DET1975.htm }}</ref>這年紅襪隊順利闖進世界大賽，不過最後7場比賽輸給紅人。<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.newspapers.com/clip/15485840/combination_of_rice_lynn_unmatched_in/ |title=Combination of Rice, Lynn unmatched in baseball |agency=[[Associated_Press|AP]] |newspaper=[[The_Arizona_Republic|The Arizona Republic]] |location=[[Phoenix,_Arizona|Phoenix, Arizona]] |date=August 17, 1979 |accessdate=November 30, 2017 |via=newspapers.com |archive-date=2017-12-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171201082240/https://www.newspapers.com/clip/15485840/combination_of_rice_lynn_unmatched_in/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>而林恩在系列賽的打擊率為2成80，並敲出1轟與5分打點。

1978年至1980年，林恩蟬聯金手套獎。1979年，他拿下美聯打擊王，並在MVP票選拿下第四名。1975年至1980年，林恩都有入選明星賽。而他在1980年5月13日達成完全打擊。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.retrosheet.org/boxesetc/1980/B05130BOS1980.htm |title=Boston Red Sox 10, Minnesota Twins 5 |website=[[Retrosheet|Retrosheet]] |date=May 13, 1980 |accessdate=2020-09-29 |archive-date=2015-09-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924135830/http://www.retrosheet.org/boxesetc/1980/B05130BOS1980.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.masslive.com/redsox/index.ssf/2015/06/list_of_the_20_boston_red_sox.html |title=List of the 20 Boston Red Sox players who have hit for the cycle starting with Brock Holt |first=Christopher |last=Smith |website=masslive.com |date=June 17, 2015 |accessdate=October 19, 2017 |archive-date=2018-06-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180612184523/https://www.masslive.com/redsox/index.ssf/2015/06/list_of_the_20_boston_red_sox.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

林恩在紅襪7個球季，打擊率為3成08，合計敲出124轟與521分打點。
===加州天使===
1981年1月，紅襪將林恩和Steve Renko交易至天使，換來Frank Tanana、Jim Dorsey和Joe Rudi等三名球員。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.nytimes.com/1981/01/24/sports/angels-obtain-lynn-from-the-red-sox-for-tanana-rudi.html |title=Angels Obtain Lynn from the Red Sox for Tanana, Rudi |first=Joseph |last=Durso |newspaper=[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]] |date=January 24, 1981 |accessdate=November 30, 2017 |archive-date=2020-02-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200228205508/https://www.nytimes.com/1981/01/24/sports/angels-obtain-lynn-from-the-red-sox-for-tanana-rudi.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>這年林恩因為膝傷困擾僅出賽76場比賽，打擊率僅2成19，並敲出5轟與31分打點。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.upi.com/Archives/1981/09/24/Sports-Briefs/6216370152000/ |title=Sports Briefs |agency=[[United_Press_International|UPI]] |website=upi.com |date=September 24, 1981 |accessdate=November 30, 2017 |archive-date=2017-12-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171201081858/https://www.upi.com/Archives/1981/09/24/Sports-Briefs/6216370152000/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>不過他在隔年繳出2成99的打擊率，差點突破3成大關。後面兩年他的打擊率分別為2成72和2成71。

1982年的美聯冠軍賽，天使隊雖然以2勝3敗輸球，不過林恩拿下了系列賽的MVP。他也成為史上第一位拿下聯盟冠軍賽MVP，球隊最後卻輸球的球員。1983年的明星賽，林恩拿下了MVP。總計他在天使隊四年，打擊率為2成71，一共敲出71轟與270分打點。

1981年，Lawrence Ritter和Donald Honig在其出版的書籍《史上最傑出的百大棒球員》中，將林恩納入其中。<ref>{{cite book |first1=Lawrence |last1=Ritter |first2=Donald |last2=Honig |title=The 100 Greatest Baseball Players of All Time |publisher=[[Crown_Publishing_Group|Crown Publishers]] |date=1981 |asin=B002XGBODQ |url=https://www.amazon.com/100-Greatest-Baseball-Players-Time/dp/B002XGBODQ/ |access-date=2020-09-29 |archive-date=2021-03-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210309022838/https://www.amazon.com/100-Greatest-Baseball-Players-Time/dp/B002XGBODQ/ }}</ref>
===巴爾的摩金鶯===
1984年，成為自由球員的林恩和金鶯隊簽下5年680萬美元的合約。<ref>[https://www.upi.com/Archives/1984/12/11/Orioles-sign-Lynn-to-five-year-pact/2025471589200/ Doherty, Robert. "Orioles sign Lynn to five-year pact," ''United Press International (UPI)'', Tuesday, December 11, 1984.] {{Wayback|url=https://www.upi.com/Archives/1984/12/11/Orioles-sign-Lynn-to-five-year-pact/2025471589200/ |date=20190810065844 }} Retrieved August 10, 2019</ref><ref>[https://www.nytimes.com/1984/12/12/sports/lynn-gets-5-year-oriole-pact.html "Lynn Gets 5-Year Oriole Pact," ''The Associated Press (AP)'', Wednesday, December 12, 1984.] {{Wayback|url=https://www.nytimes.com/1984/12/12/sports/lynn-gets-5-year-oriole-pact.html |date=20190810093115 }} Retrieved August 10, 2019</ref>當時球隊還另外簽下Lee Lacy與Don Aase等兩位老將，不過金鶯卻在1986年與1988年於美聯敬陪末座。<ref>[https://www.latimes.com/archives/la-xpm-1988-04-22-sp-2099-story.html Newhan, Ross. "Who's Been Minding the Farm?: Robinson Says Orioles Stopped Developing Championship Talent," ''Los Angeles Times'', Friday, April 22, 1988.] {{Wayback|url=https://www.latimes.com/archives/la-xpm-1988-04-22-sp-2099-story.html |date=20190810081148 }} Retrieved August 10, 2019</ref><ref>[https://www.latimes.com/archives/la-xpm-1985-07-03-sp-10318-story.html Povich, Shirley. "Williams Tries to Buy a Flag for Baltimore: Orioles Still Trailing Despite Adding Weaver, Lynn, Aase," ''The Washington Post'', Wednesday, July 3, 1985.] {{Wayback|url=https://www.latimes.com/archives/la-xpm-1985-07-03-sp-10318-story.html |date=20190810065845 }} Retrieved August 10, 2019</ref>而林恩也曾取笑金鶯球帽的樣子非常滑稽，他說他從未見過會有球隊會在球帽上放上卡通鳥類的圖案。<ref>[https://www.sun-sentinel.com/news/fl-xpm-1991-05-19-9102270476-story.html Hyde, Dave. "And It's Suit, Suit, Suit for the Ho-o-o-me Team," ''Sun-Sentinel'' (Fort Lauderdale, FL), Sunday, May 19, 1991.] {{Wayback|url=https://www.sun-sentinel.com/news/fl-xpm-1991-05-19-9102270476-story.html |date=20190810073048 }} Retrieved August 10, 2019</ref>合計他在金鶯隊的打擊率為2成65，一共敲出87轟與232分打點。
===底特律老虎===
1988年8月31日，金鶯隊用林恩向老虎隊交易Chris Hoiles、Cesar Mejia和Robinson Garces。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://sabr.org/bioproj/person/7fb674d5 |title=Fred Lynn |first=Tom |last=Nahigian |website=[[Society_for_American_Baseball_Research|Society for American Baseball Research]] |accessdate=March 19, 2018 |archive-date=2020-04-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200423174721/https://sabr.org/bioproj/person/7fb674d5 |dead-url=no }}</ref>不過當時發生一段小插曲，原已完成交易的林恩並沒有在當天到球隊報到，因此大聯盟宣布林恩不得出席季後賽的賽事。但是大聯盟主席Peter Ueberroth後來推翻了這個判決，他認為只要交易成功球員就不受出賽場次的限制。<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.newspapers.com/clip/15491638/lynn_playoff_ban_to_be_lifted/ |title=Lynn playoff ban to be lifted |first=Jerome |last=Holtzman |newspaper=[[Chicago_Tribune|Chicago Tribune]] |date=September 8, 1988 |accessdate=November 30, 2017 |via=newspapers.com |archive-date=2017-12-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171201131516/https://www.newspapers.com/clip/15491638/lynn_playoff_ban_to_be_lifted/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>然而老虎隊依舊以1場勝差輸給紅襪隊，無緣晉級季後賽。

該年林恩在老虎隊出賽27場比賽，打擊率為2成22，並敲出7轟與19分打點。隔年他出賽119場比賽，打擊率為2成41，並敲出11轟與46分打點。球季結束後他成為自由球員。
===聖地牙哥教士===
1989年12月，林恩加盟教士隊，這也是他首度轉戰國聯球隊。1990年，38歲的他繳出2成40的打擊率，外帶6轟與23分打點的成績。球季結束後他成為自由球員，雖然他繼續維持體態以便隨時重返大聯盟，不過並未有球隊給他春訓邀請，教士隊便成了林恩職業生涯的最終站。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.newspapers.com/clip/15492182/fred_lynn_adjusts_to_life_out_of/ |title=Fred Lynn adjusts to life out of baseball |newspaper=[[The_Greenville_News|The Greenville News]] |location=[[Greenville,_South_Carolina|Greenville, South Carolina]] |date=June 20, 1991 |accessdate=November 30, 2017 |via=newspapers.com |archive-date=2017-12-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171201181953/https://www.newspapers.com/clip/15492182/fred_lynn_adjusts_to_life_out_of/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>
